Photo by TeachersForTeachers on August 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Attention High School Teachers! We're looking for teachers who want to make an impact outside of the classroom!'.

Photo by TeachersForTeachers on August 20, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Teachlikeyoumeanit @teachlikeyou A student said to me this week, "I think the reason we can all focus in your class is because you give us time to be silly and hyper, and you're silly with us so when it's time to focus, we focus." Thought provoking feedback from a middle schooler.'.

node.text: @Kamiapp wants to help you get your #BacktoSchool wishlist fulfilled, so head on over, give Kami a follow and let them know what you need for the school year!
